--divider-pattern-url);mask-image:var(--divider-pattern-url)}.elementor-widget-divider--no-spacing{--divider-pattern-size:auto}.elementor-widget-divider--bg-round{--divider-pattern-repeat:round}.rtl .elementor-widget-divider .elementor-divider__text{direction:rtl}.e-con-inner>.elementor-widget-divider,.e-con>.elementor-widget-divider{width:var(--container-widget-width,100%);--flex-grow:var(--container-widget-flex-grow)}<\/style>\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"vamtam-has-theme-widget-styles elementor-element elementor-element-0ef2750 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0ef2750\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Responsibilities<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f2b0e8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7f2b0e8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00b7 Develop and execute digital advertising strategies on platforms such as Google Ads, Meta Ads, LinkedIn Ads, Twitter Ads, as well as explore and test new emerging channels.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Conduct keyword research, competitive analysis, and audience segmentation to optimize campaigns across all channels.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Identify and evaluate opportunities in alternative paid media channels, such as podcasts, streaming platforms, specialized websites, among others.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Collaborate with other teams to explore and leverage new digital advertising opportunities outside of traditional channels.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Monitor and analyze key performance metrics across all channels, adapting strategies as needed to improve results.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Stay updated on the latest trends and best practices in digital advertising and continuously explore new opportunities in the evolving media landscape.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a8ea016 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"a8ea016\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"vamtam-has-theme-widget-styles elementor-element elementor-element-a65b6cb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a65b6cb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Requirements<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-934de02 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"934de02\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00b7 Demonstrable experience in managing paid advertising campaigns across multiple digital platforms, with an emphasis on exploring alternative channels.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Deep knowledge of tools like Google Ads, Facebook Business Manager, LinkedIn Campaign Manager, Twitter Ads Manager, as well as experience in evaluating and adopting new platforms.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Strong analytical skills and the ability to interpret data to make decisions across all paid media channels.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Excellent verbal and written communication skills.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Ability to work independently and as part of a team in a dynamic environment.<\/p><p>\u00b7 Certifications in Google Ads and other digital advertising platforms are a plus.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-575ff47 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"575ff47\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"vamtam-has-theme-widget-styles elementor-element elementor-element-4f3d971 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4f3d971\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Compensation<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92b25b1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"92b25b1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This is a 100% on-site position. Our offices are located near of Quinta de Olivos, and we offer spacious and comfortable spaces. Additionally, there is a kitchen available for breakfast, a dining room, a rest area, and all services.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d2684a elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"8d2684a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"vamtam-has-theme-widget-styles elementor-element elementor-element-cd23c5a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cd23c5a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How to Apply<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e486e74 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e486e74\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To apply, please email <a href=\"mailto:careers@spaceplus.tech\">careers@spaceplus.tech<\/a>, including your resume and portfolio. To test your attention to detail and show that you&#8217;ve read this entire listing, please also share your favorite typeface and explain why it resonates with you.<\/p><p>We are interested in hearing from individual applicants and kindly request that recruiters, agencies, and offshore firms refrain from applying.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6690789 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6690789\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>* SpacePlus is committed to equal employment opportunities and does not discriminate against any employee or applicant for employment based on factors such as race, color, religion, national origin, age, gender, sex, ancestry, citizenship status, mental or physical disability, genetic information, sexual orientation, veteran status, or military status. We actively seek individuals to join our team and do not engage with recruiters, agencies, or offshore firms in our hiring process.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We&#8217;re looking for a hunter to help us contact to the world.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"tags":[65],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/988575"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=988575"}],"version-history":[{"count":23,"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/988575\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":989517,"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/988575\/revisions\/989517"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=988575"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=988575"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/spaceplus.tech\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=988575"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}